                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7755" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1941</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1247 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">失落的黑井，永恒的白盐——国投赋能千年盐都变身记</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Lost Heijing, The Eternal Salt——The story of the Transformation of the Millennium Salt City Empowered by SDIC</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵书虹，孔营营，杨兰，杨越琴，杨雨婷，李晓光，李佳懿，白梦，倪向丽（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南省黑井古镇旅游开发有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑井古镇；旅游产业融合；发展战略；特色小镇；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Heijing Ancient Town; Integration of tourism industry; Development strategy; Characteristic town</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑井，一个位于云南省楚雄州禄丰市龙川江畔的古镇，2000多年的经济和文化变迁，为黑井留下丰厚的盐历史和盐文化。黑井古镇于1995开始发展旅游，并在2010年达到旅游经济发展的鼎盛期。但是，国内兴起建设特色旅游小镇浪潮使得市场竞争加剧，黑井古镇旅游发展成效大不如从前。如何解决当下黑井古镇旅游发展所面临的困境、采取何种策略恢复黑井古镇的旅游活力？丁经理带领团队又开始了新的探索。案例以主人公丁庆萍的视角描述了黑井古镇旅游由盛转衰、再次开启创新发展的历程，也是她本人从导游向经营管理人员成功转型的故事，期望通过本案例帮助学员深入理解“旅游地生命周期”、“产业发展模式”、“产业融合”等知识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Heijing, an ancient town located on the banks of the Longchuan River in Lufeng City, Chuxiong Prefecture, Yunnan Province, has been undergoing economic and cultural changes for more than 2,000 years, leaving behind a rich salt history and salt culture for Heijing. Heijing Ancient Town started to develop tourism in 1995, and reached the peak of tourism economic development in 2010. However, the rise of the wave of construction of characteristic tourist towns in China has intensified market competition, and the tourism development of Heijing Ancient Town has not achieved much in the past. How to solve the current predicament that Heijing Ancient Town is facing in tourism development, and what strategy should be adopted to restore the tourism vitality of Heijing Ancient Town? Manager Ding led the team to start a new exploration. From the perspective of the protagonist Ding Qingping, the case describes the process of the ancient town&#39;s tourism from prosperity to decline, and then to innovation and development again. It is also the story of her successful transformation from a tour guide to a management staff. It is hoped that this case will help students gain a deep understanding of the knowledge of &quot;tourist destination life cycle&quot;, &quot;industrial development model&quot;, and &quot;industrial integration&quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《旅游市场营销》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">旅游地生命周期；旅游产品开发；战略环境分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
